@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT_TOKEN
@accountId = 1
@externalToken = REPLACE_WITH_ACCOUNT_TOKEN
@packageId = 1
@adminUserId = 1
@contentSlug = getting-started-with-hyperpay
@previewToken = REPLACE_WITH_PREVIEW_TOKEN

### Health - Kiểm tra service sống
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###
### Auth - Đăng ký
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "full_name": "Nguyen Van A"
}

###
### Auth - Đăng nhập
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

###
### Auth - Quên mật khẩu
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com"
}

###
### Users - Lấy thông tin profile hiện tại
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Accounts - Tạo tài khoản ngân hàng (trả account + token)
### Lưu ý: sẽ bị chặn nếu bank không thuộc package hiện tại hoặc vượt limit bank types
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "bank_name": "VCB",
  "account_number": "0123456789",
  "account_holder": "Nguyen Van A"
}

###
### Accounts - Danh sách tài khoản của user
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Accounts - Refresh API token cho 1 account
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}/token/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Transactions (internal) - Lịch sử giao dịch theo account qua JWT
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Transactions (external) - Lịch sử giao dịch theo account token
GET {{baseUrl}}/external/accounts/{{externalToken}}/transactions

###
### Transactions (external) - Tạo giao dịch (consume quota package + trigger webhook nếu cấu hình)
POST {{baseUrl}}/external/accounts/{{externalToken}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 250000,
  "type": "credit",
  "description": "Nap tien vi",
  "payment_code": "HPY12345678",
  "balance": 1000000,
  "occurred_at": "2026-03-11T09:30:00.000Z"
}

###
### Banks - Tạo ngân hàng
POST {{baseUrl}}/banks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Vietcombank",
  "code": "VCB",
  "icon_url": "https://example.com/icons/vcb.png"
}

###
### Banks - Danh sách ngân hàng
GET {{baseUrl}}/banks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Plans - Tạo gói dịch vụ
POST {{baseUrl}}/plans
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Basic",
  "price_vnd": 99000,
  "max_bank_accounts": 5,
  "max_transactions": 1000,
  "duration_days": 30,
  "description": "Goi co ban cho ca nhan",
  "bank_ids": [1, 2]
}

###
### Plans - Danh sách gói dịch vụ
GET {{baseUrl}}/plans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Packages - Tạo package (Admin only)
### Lưu ý: endpoint này yêu cầu role ADMIN (403 nếu không đủ quyền)
POST {{baseUrl}}/packages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Starter Package",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "is_default": true,
  "default_start_at": "2026-03-11T00:00:00.000Z",
  "default_end_at": "2026-12-31T23:59:59.000Z",
  "price_vnd": 149000,
  "max_transactions": 5000,
  "max_webhook_deliveries": 10000,
  "max_bank_types": 3,
  "duration_days": 30,
  "description": "Goi cho merchant nho",
  "bank_ids": [1, 2, 3]
}

###
### Packages - Danh sách package khả dụng
GET {{baseUrl}}/packages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Packages - Ví dụ package unlimited (0 = không giới hạn)
POST {{baseUrl}}/packages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Unlimited Package",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "is_default": false,
  "price_vnd": 999000,
  "max_transactions": 0,
  "max_webhook_deliveries": 0,
  "max_bank_types": 0,
  "duration_days": 30,
  "description": "Goi khong gioi han toan bo",
  "bank_ids": []
}

###
### Packages - User mua package
POST {{baseUrl}}/packages/{{packageId}}/purchase
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "duration_id": 1
}

# duration_id: ID mốc thời gian (từ GET /durations). Giá và số ngày lấy từ bảng package_duration_prices + durations.
###
### Packages - Gói active hiện tại của user
GET {{baseUrl}}/packages/me/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Durations - Danh sách mốc thời gian mua (dùng cho modal mua gói)
GET {{baseUrl}}/durations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# Response: [{ "id", "name", "months", "days", "sort_order" }]

###
### Webhook - Lấy cấu hình webhook hiện tại
GET {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Webhook - Xóa cấu hình webhook (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Webhook - Tạo/cập nhật cấu hình webhook (upsert 1 webhook của user)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "url": "https://your-system.com/webhooks/hyperpay",
  "secret_token": "your-webhook-secret",
  "account_ids": [1, 2],
  "transaction_direction": "IN",
  "retry_on_non_2xx": true,
  "max_retry_attempts": 3,
  "content_type": "JSON",
  "auth_type": "BEARER",
  "auth_bearer_token": "token-from-target-system",
  "require_payment_code": true,
  "payment_code_rule_enabled": true,
  "payment_code_prefix": "HPY",
  "payment_code_suffix_min_length": 8,
  "payment_code_suffix_max_length": 12,
  "payment_code_suffix_charset": "NUMERIC",
  "is_active": true
}

###
### Webhook - Ví dụ auth BASIC
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "url": "https://your-system.com/webhooks/hyperpay",
  "secret_token": "your-webhook-secret",
  "auth_type": "BASIC",
  "auth_username": "webhook_user",
  "auth_password": "webhook_password",
  "is_active": true
}

###
### Webhook - Ví dụ auth HEADER
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "url": "https://your-system.com/webhooks/hyperpay",
  "secret_token": "your-webhook-secret",
  "auth_type": "HEADER",
  "auth_header_name": "X-HYPERPAY-TOKEN",
  "auth_header_value": "token-from-target-system",
  "is_active": true
}

###
### Content Public - Danh sách bài viết/docs/help đã publish
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/content?type=BLOG_POST&limit=10&offset=0

###
### Content Public - Filter theo category + tag + search
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/content?type=DOC_PAGE&category=api-reference&tag=payments&q=webhook

###
### Content Public - Chi tiết theo slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/content/{{contentSlug}}

###
### Content Public - Danh sách categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/content/categories

###
### Content Public - Danh sách tags
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/content/tags

###
### Content Admin - Tạo/Cập nhật Category
### Lưu ý: yêu cầu role EDITOR/ADMIN (403 nếu không đủ quyền)
POST {{baseUrl}}/content/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "API Reference",
  "slug": "api-reference",
  "description": "Tai lieu ky thuat API"
}

###
### Content Admin - Tạo/Cập nhật Tag
### Lưu ý: yêu cầu role EDITOR/ADMIN (403 nếu không đủ quyền)
POST {{baseUrl}}/content/tags
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Payments",
  "slug": "payments",
  "description": "Noi dung lien quan thanh toan"
}

###
### Content Admin - Danh sách Category cho quản trị
GET {{baseUrl}}/content/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Content Admin - Cập nhật Category theo slug
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/content/categories/api-reference
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "API Reference Updated",
  "slug": "api-reference",
  "description": "Tai lieu ky thuat API va webhook"
}

###
### Content Admin - Xóa mềm Category theo slug
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/content/categories/api-reference
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Content Admin - Danh sách Tag cho quản trị
GET {{baseUrl}}/content/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Content Admin - Cập nhật Tag theo slug
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/content/tags/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Payments Updated",
  "slug": "payments",
  "description": "Tag cho noi dung thanh toan"
}

###
### Content Admin - Xóa mềm Tag theo slug
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/content/tags/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Content Admin - Tạo bài/blog/docs/help (draft)
### Lưu ý: yêu cầu role EDITOR/ADMIN (403 nếu không đủ quyền)
POST {{baseUrl}}/content
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "type": "BLOG_POST",
  "title": "HyperPay webhook best practices",
  "slug": "hyperpay-webhook-best-practices",
  "excerpt": "Huong dan trien khai webhook an toan",
  "content": "Noi dung markdown/html tai day...",
  "cover_image": "https://example.com/cover/webhook.png",
  "seo_title": "HyperPay webhook best practices",
  "seo_description": "Checklist webhook production cho HyperPay",
  "seo_keywords": "hyperpay, webhook, security",
  "scheduled_publish_at": "2026-03-12T10:00:00.000Z",
  "category_slugs": ["api-reference", "integration"],
  "tag_slugs": ["payments", "webhook", "security"]
}

###
### Content Admin - Cập nhật + publish + taxonomy
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/content/{{contentSlug}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "SCHEDULED",
  "title": "HyperPay webhook best practices (updated)",
  "seo_keywords": "hyperpay, webhook",
  "scheduled_publish_at": "2026-03-13T10:00:00.000Z",
  "category_slugs": ["api-reference"],
  "tag_slugs": ["payments", "webhook"]
}

###
### Content Admin - Danh sách quản trị (filter type/status/taxonomy/search)
GET {{baseUrl}}/content?type=BLOG_POST&status=DRAFT&category=api-reference&tag=webhook&q=hyperpay&limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Content Admin - Tạo preview token cho draft/scheduled
POST {{baseUrl}}/content/{{contentSlug}}/preview-token
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "expires_in_minutes": 30
}

###
### Content Public - Xem preview bằng token
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/content/preview/{{previewToken}}

###
### Content Admin - Lấy danh sách revision của 1 bài
GET {{baseUrl}}/content/{{contentSlug}}/revisions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Content Admin - Restore 1 revision
POST {{baseUrl}}/content/{{contentSlug}}/revisions/1/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Content Admin - Soft delete theo slug
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/content/{{contentSlug}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Negative test - Webhook BEARER thiếu auth_bearer_token (expected 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "url": "https://your-system.com/webhooks/hyperpay",
  "secret_token": "your-webhook-secret",
  "auth_type": "BEARER"
}

###
### Negative test - Webhook HEADER thiếu auth_header_value (expected 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "url": "https://your-system.com/webhooks/hyperpay",
  "secret_token": "your-webhook-secret",
  "auth_type": "HEADER",
  "auth_header_name": "X-HYPERPAY-TOKEN"
}

###
### Negative test - Payment code rule sai min/max (expected 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "url": "https://your-system.com/webhooks/hyperpay",
  "secret_token": "your-webhook-secret",
  "payment_code_rule_enabled": true,
  "payment_code_prefix": "HPY",
  "payment_code_suffix_min_length": 12,
  "payment_code_suffix_max_length": 8,
  "payment_code_suffix_charset": "NUMERIC"
}

###
### Negative test - Content preview token quá nhỏ (expected 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/content/{{contentSlug}}/preview-token
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "expires_in_minutes": 1
}

###
### =========================
### ADMIN APIs (ADMIN only)
### =========================

###
### Admin - Users list
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users?q=user&limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Admin - Update user role
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/{{adminUserId}}/role
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "role": "EDITOR"
}

###
### Admin - Plans list
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/plans?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Admin - Create plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/plans
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Admin Plan",
  "price_vnd": 199000,
  "max_bank_accounts": 5,
  "max_transactions": 2000,
  "duration_days": 30,
  "description": "Plan created from admin API"
}

###
### Admin - Update plan
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/plans/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "max_transactions": 2500
}

###
### Admin - Packages list (có pricing theo từng duration)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/packages?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Admin - Create package (không còn duration_days; bắt buộc pricing theo duration)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/packages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Starter Package",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "price_vnd": 149000,
  "max_transactions": 5000,
  "max_webhook_deliveries": 10000,
  "description": "Goi cho merchant nho",
  "banks": [
    { "bank_id": 1, "account_limit": 2 },
    { "bank_id": 2, "account_limit": 1 }
  ],
  "pricing": [
    { "duration_id": 1, "price_vnd": 149000 },
    { "duration_id": 2, "price_vnd": 400000 },
    { "duration_id": 3, "price_vnd": 750000 },
    { "duration_id": 4, "price_vnd": 1400000 }
  ]
}

###
### Admin - Update package (pricing: thay thế toàn bộ nếu gửi lên)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/packages/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "pricing": [
    { "duration_id": 1, "price_vnd": 159000 },
    { "duration_id": 2, "price_vnd": 420000 }
  ]
}

###
### Admin - Durations list
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/durations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Admin - Create duration (mốc thời gian: 1 tháng, 3 tháng, ...)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/durations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "1 tháng",
  "months": 1,
  "days": 30,
  "sort_order": 1
}

###
### Admin - Update duration
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/durations/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "1 tháng (ưu đãi)",
  "days": 31
}

###
### Admin - Delete duration (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/durations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Admin - Banks list
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/banks?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Admin - Create bank
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/banks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Example Bank",
  "code": "EXB",
  "icon_url": "https://example.com/exb.png"
}

###
### Admin - Update bank
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/banks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Example Bank Updated"
}

###
### Admin - User packages list
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/user-packages?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Admin - Assign package for user
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/user-packages/assign
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "user_id": {{adminUserId}},
  "package_id": {{packageId}},
  "duration_days": 30,
  "status": "active"
}

###
### Admin - Update user package status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/user-packages/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "suspended"
}

###
### Admin - Webhooks list (global)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/webhooks?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Admin - Transactions list (global)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/transactions?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
